    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-12T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-12T18:00:00-05:00" n="642"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d642">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 654.119/157a</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SPA1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stovall</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d642fn1">The same, on the same date, to the
                        Ambassador in Argentina (No. 536) and the Minister in Venezuela (No.
                        636).</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-12T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1918, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1604. For the purpose of obtaining greater tonnage to facilitate the movement of
                    the wheat crop from South America and thus hasten the relief in wheat promised
                    to Switzerland, War Trade Board has placed a temporary prohibition upon the
                    importation of corn from overseas.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_PFL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
